reviewText: I gave this 4 stars and regret I gave 5 to the other one. Remaster these please! Otherwise imminently watchable. The Alex Toth art work is beautiful to behold. I also like the music which I found wonderfully moody.  I intend to eventually get them all.
I loved "Space Angel" as a kid.  This DVD brought back some fond memories of good times I spent watching the show.
These are some of the great early cartoons. The picture and sound quality was very good.
